732021f-a.title: Islands - Coney Island pier - Boardwalk.
732021f-a.text:
Coney Island Pier, south of the Boardwalk at West 18th Street.
April 2, 1924.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

732022f-c.text:

(2)
The same, another view.
Jue 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
(3)
The same, showing another view of the Coney Island Pier looking
north toward the Boardwalk, showing George C. Tilyou's Steeplechase
Park in the background.
NE ~ .35E  September 6, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
